_sText:
If this map is too straining on the eyes, get the NON-animated version "de_frames"

De_framez (fixed a bug, added animated wall texture & implemented radar + overview)
Place in cs source map directory.

There are two bombsites, one at ct spawn.  20 spawn points for each team.  This map trys to focus on tactics & gameplay rather than visuals (though the visuals arnt bad - just not realistic).  Most of the map favors close in weapons, though there are a few areas where snipers will have a definate advantage.  
Entire map is made of animating brushes (except water & sky), to give a wireframe feel to it. 

Size: 8976KB
Type: Demolition
Spawns: 20 each for t's and ct's - 40 Total (Not recommended tho)
Author: Mael!
Feedback: samgilligan@gmail.com
